{"tid":1411852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨凌晨在天水圍天耀商場外，被捕人士的最近情況","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T07:55:33.000Z","uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18780d14aab79bcbe4ce8d15b731299cd8de4edd","tid":1411852,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaxqRQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaxqRQ3.jpg&h=0a7dfbb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（12:00）昨凌晨在天水圍天耀商場外，被捕人士的最近情況：<br />\n<br />\n1. 被扯甩裙及內褲的女士，已保釋（恕不公開姓氏）<br />\n<br />\n2. 兩位分別姓莫及蓋的男士，會安排去醫院驗傷，稍後保釋。<br />\n<br />\n以上三位，確實有律師跟進。<br />\n<br />\n另外，兩位男士及最後一位被捕女士，因一直未能找到全名，律師沒辦法跟進，如有消息，麻煩聯絡我。 <br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n<br />\n8月3日（星期六）晚在旺角彌敦道及亞皆老街交界被捕的示威者，將於今日下午兩時半在九龍城裁判法院上庭，暫時我範圍內（五位）確實控告非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n有其他最新情況，再報。大家平平安安。"},{"pid":"95e435178cf2719ad5ffed1b1d4cbcaebc65250c","tid":1411852,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c646a8fee453b3fc0d3d3082b391301cf7e3d52","tid":1411852,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"另外，兩位男士及最後一位被捕女士，因一直未能找到全名，律師沒辦法跟進<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48da1c5d5c11c9bd6819b527c501a2ef52c69da","tid":1411852,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c407ab1b0cf59a526545704942c22408bb4c555","tid":1411852,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"蟲太好球"},{"pid":"31da0f8f6cb4c775154b0baeafe1f32df73bb52f","tid